author: Dimensional.Wabbit
text:
Tonight I'll be thinking of you.
Thinking of your hands finding your favorite places.
  My body excited and begging for your touch.

Light gasps for air, your name lingering on my lips.

 I can hardly bare my imagination, these forbidden thoughts, and the things you'll do to me..

author: Dimensional.Wabbit
text:
When all those things are gone, and your old and grey.
  Be sure to know the communication is why I will stay. 
The communication of heart to heart.
     You can take my arms, my eyes, my ears, but in the end It will always be the connection.

author: Dimensional.Wabbit
text:
Yeah, you're cute but can we sit and discuss life's big issues?
   Always keep in mind looks, youth, beauty are all temporary.
    Don't waste my time with ass shaking, and the amount of reps you do at the gym.
I am not a temporary fix, I am a forever kind of love.

author: Dimensional.Wabbit
text:
I sent the rain and you buried it in lightning.
  I tried to damped the current and you tried to spark the flame.
    There's no escaping a love like this.

The universe extends to make sure we know what inevitable truly means.

author: Dimensional.Wabbit
text:
You show your son a better way, make him the best of humanity, the way you couldn't be.
         -The Doctor

author: Dimensional.Wabbit
text:
I hold this deep prayer to reach your heart.
  I need it more than any new start.
A tragic move does stir my heart.
   The struggle to do always, what's right.

author: Dimensional.Wabbit
text:
Silence beckons.
  Strange I am in no mood to challenge it.
    My heart a bit uneasy.
My grip a little less.
Even if you might be angry, I still reach to you for solace.
   Encourage you to have a moment for yourself.
      Need me, I am astonished.
Always yours.
